{"tid":630441,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係我73歲的生日","createTime":"2018-04-15T15:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T17:46:29.000Z","uid":100347,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a219b503e440f35790168c8e6d1858bd5191465","tid":630441,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:15:30.000Z","msg":"其實我可能係各位口中嘅廢老<br />\n<br />\n冇人冇物<br />\n<br />\n你地平日在公園會見到一D老人 呆坐成個下晝 可能果個就係我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每日坐定定發呆，回憶以前快樂的事，重覆又重覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好掛住家人、好掛住朋友<br />\n<br />\n只可以係回憶同發夢見到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n各位 好好珍惜對你好嘅人<br />\n<br />\n對自己唔好嘅人 除非你去報仇，否則唔需要放佢地上心"},{"pid":"0bdd5fc2836b0d96f37d320c6f91b808ed187ff1","tid":630441,"uid":126690,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:27:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e03a8e7e06e7fdf4fc06436ceedea3e34fe1c92e","tid":630441,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"我都係廢老，幾時約出黎去公園一齊捉象棋"},{"pid":"d76974c798ff53de6efb6562fa96fe42757568f9","tid":630441,"uid":165024,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/232908_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F232908_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=df69ff09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04a0b780f86f51eef4481440e743ae6e9a59c4e0","tid":630441,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e03a8e7e06e7fdf4fc06436ceedea3e34fe1c92e","tid":630441,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:29:08.000Z","msg":"我都係廢老，幾時約出黎去公園一齊捉象棋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"一齊？放狗<img src=\"/